        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on his visit to N. Wales and the evidence of glaciation, of which he feels certain.</p>
            <p>His marine theory [of the parallel roads of Glen Roy] has revived after Louis Agassiz’s "ice work" knocked it on the head.</p>
        </abstract>
